Package: farsfunctions
Type: Package
Title: Analyse FARS Data
Version: 1.1.0
Author: Viren Dias
Maintainer: Viren Dias <chootyviren@gmail.com>
Description: This package has several functions that can; read a FARS CSV file and
    return a data frame of detailed information about accidents that occured in a
    specified year, summarize accidents that have occurred in each month across
    several specified years, and plot accidents on a geographical map of a
    specified US state for a specified year.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: dplyr,
    tidyr,
    readr,
    magrittr,
    maps,
    graphics
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
